title: Laundry in Unit! Studio apartment  Lincoln Park
posting_body: ['Incredible Studio with laundry in the unit!', 'Update open space apartment!', 'The kitchen features are stainless steel appliances, granite countertop dishwasher, fridge, microwave and stove, large cabinets.', 'Fitness room, elevator building.', 'Great location 5 min walking to red/brown/purple line train station at Fullerton, convenience public transportation across the street.', 'Walking distance to groceries stores, restaurants, bars, boutiques and the lakefront.', 'Pet friendly', 'Pictures may not be the actual unit.', 'Prices are subject to change.', 'Call and Text Sylvia Romero from Apartment Guys (312) 468-3409.', 'Reference number']
